data.description: Welcome to 2115 S 10th St. An inviting 2 story, 4-bed, 1-bath house with a sprawling 3-sided wraparound deck is looking for new owners! The spacious kitchen, with included appliances and a serving station unfolds to a large, open layout. Sunlit hardwood floors grace the large open living and dining area. A spacious main-level bedroom and a full bath with a whirlpool tiled shower enhance comfort. Upstairs, discover three bedrooms, each with ample closets and an additional storage space. Outside, a private backyard and a generous entertaining deck create a quiet retreat. An extra-deep one-car garage and a 2-car concrete parking, poised for a new garage. Welcome home! Seller at seller's expense to update electrical.
